reviews.text: 食物精致 魚生有水準 貴價優質的日本菜

Lunched here for omakase. Nice Meal with fresh fish and seafood. The roll is full of meshed tuna and rich in texture by tempura crust. However the chef seems not friendly and lack of introduction on the food and dishes.
Food quality is great, service needs to be improved. The waiter can be rude.
旺角食啲日本野通常都係放題，呢一間係少數唔係食放題，中午食飯嘅好選擇，環境好舒服。

價錢較高但合理. 
食物賣相好質素高, 壽司的生魚片新鮮味美, 值得推介。
